{"tid":469653,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"藍染一個人單挑零番隊5個人贏到嗎","createTime":"2017-11-15T13:56:31.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-16T16:39:25.000Z","uid":68626,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"25592473ea51c25372b7040728208c1d74b95e0a","tid":469653,"uid":68626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T13:56:31.000Z","msg":"和尚好似可以打贏藍染<br />\n但藍染同崩玉融合左之後又好似宇宙無敵咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b16353287ebfc3350f863f7f9497bef1af60ca67","tid":469653,"uid":54025,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T14:52:03.000Z","msg":"其實藍染咁勁點解要崩玉?<br />\n<br />\n直接鏡花水月再斬撚死晒班仆街味得"},{"pid":"b34394b3ac8547fe61ff1dd65f0d8bc3623bcad8","tid":469653,"uid":20544,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T17:50:02.000Z","msg":"其實和尚個能力都好屈<br />\n佢只要奪走佐「鏡花水月」呢個名<br />\n就算中緊幻術都即刻冇效化啦"},{"pid":"d113c7f3bed8bf69e1e78be03b208c8393ed745f","tid":469653,"uid":21917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T18:00:54.000Z","msg":"無崩玉一定輸 因為0番隊無人中過鏡花 藍染就係知死神有極限先想突破姐"},{"pid":"e9dafc98dad79ed3864f0e962e2460a93f7b3975","tid":469653,"uid":68626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T04:35:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實藍染咁勁點解要崩玉?<br />\n<br />\n直接鏡花水月再斬撚死晒班仆街味得</blockquote><br />\n佢打完隊長之後<br />\n打一護老豆已經唔夠打<br />\n一心仲串鳩佢話佢動作慢左<br />\n佢都話自己已經到左死神極限<br />\n不過一個人挑晒成個死神界就真係死神極限"},{"pid":"e01d2c4179037939ce0d4e374cb569519fe8bbe1","tid":469653,"uid":91931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T04:48:28.000Z","msg":"咁就真係要睇卍解係咩能力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d387d19c9ab7f8b497960a6efd81ba97384f4fd3","tid":469653,"uid":54025,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T04:55:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁就真係要睇卍解係咩能力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n可能仲廢過雀蜂雷公鞭<br />\n<br />\n所以廢時提"},{"pid":"b42006e9a5ad8a3451ad83e5ecfd463575e16663","tid":469653,"uid":25028,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T05:04:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實和尚個能力都好屈<br />\n佢只要奪走佐「鏡花水月」呢個名<br />\n就算中緊幻術都即刻冇效化啦</blockquote><br />\n藍柒唔止鏡花勁 佢連個本體都勁撚到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a79c8567a8301f88da142b073a3fb1b3d9c93c6f","tid":469653,"uid":82889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T05:57:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實和尚個能力都好屈<br />\n佢只要奪走佐「鏡花水月」呢個名<br />\n就算中緊幻術都即刻冇效化啦</blockquote><br />\n你幾時產生左奪走左鏡花水月個名既幻覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a267ca205d06653ea79c749ab86c3310e0dd38e","tid":469653,"uid":82404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T09:50:57.000Z","msg":"和尚係屈<br />\n但藍染仲屈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5dcd7b9bb929759ddc7b51ea900c30dacb0658b4","tid":469653,"uid":39,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T10:14:56.000Z","msg":"有哈 同 藍染 2個人個能力根本唔用劇情殺就無敵<br />\n藍染能力根本唔止係普通幻覺 <br />\n而係直程連你自己做緊咩同做左咩都唔知<br />\n佢要講既話 你以為自己出左招?<br />\n你以為自己見到我 ?<br />\n成堆隊長殺藍染原來係打緊雛森 <br />\n已經證明到佢幾無敵<br />\n要成隊零番隊互打都仲得 <br />\n你話佢本身係廢物 剩係屈把刀能力都算<br />\n佢本體仲要都基本上無敵"},{"pid":"5ce18957695c7066483412b9af026c21a9a38b82","tid":469653,"uid":82404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T10:19:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔係喎<br />\n零番隊未必睇過藍染始解，鏡花水月未必有效<br />\n藍染對一護都唔開，對班零番隊都未必開"},{"pid":"6bc1e04c34fb3c8de62aab0233c2df6ea151a18b","tid":469653,"uid":99978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T10:51:36.000Z","msg":"根本其餘四個咩能力都唔知<br />\n就被d所謂親衛隊殺哂<br />\non9到震<br />\n咁撚廢就唔好吹到咩戰力勁過十三隊"},{"pid":"d142cefa075c07fec18e387585170187d9222f6a","tid":469653,"uid":68394,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T11:41:56.000Z","msg":"藍染淨係用鬼道都好勁"},{"pid":"5ad74506aed334201eccaf254fcb418ebf857c1d","tid":469653,"uid":69746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T12:48:55.000Z","msg":"到今時今日我都唔知藍染點解輸俾一護<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80175f4e87f5693f05d520c78af4043989dd3c73","tid":469653,"uid":25028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T15:54:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>到今時今日我都唔知藍染點解輸俾一護<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n店長有科技封崩玉 藍染就做左on9仔 一護只係令佢露出破綻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48e527dabbc3bde0f8e88d43e28630400c51891b","tid":469653,"uid":68626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T15:55:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>到今時今日我都唔知藍染點解輸俾一護<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n店長有科技封崩玉 藍染就做左on9仔 一護只係令佢露出破綻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實係因為藍染意志動搖先輸"},{"pid":"76f4db1db7ca96c43ac67078fb7ca2838e9e7a22","tid":469653,"uid":93595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T16:39:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>到今時今日我都唔知藍染點解輸俾一護<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n店長有科技封崩玉 藍染就做左on9仔 一護只係令佢露出破綻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實係因為藍染意志動搖先輸</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n輸果個其實係藍柒<br />\n藍染孖生細佬黎"}]}